content: We have a meeting next week with a major VC—whats the best venue in Palo Alto to host the meeting?

The Palo Alto Art Center, Lucie Stern Community Center, Elks Lodge, HanaHaus, Crowne Plaza Palo Alto, Sheraton, Rengstorff House, Gamble Garden, Mooi, Club Auto Sport and Guildhouse are all venues in Palo Alto.

If you want to make a good impression, I'd recommend the Guildhouse, which is a fully customisable, high-tech event space with an industrial aesthetic and a full bar.
